Buttons
	*Tweets
		name:TweetButton
		desc:Send tweets. Probally something controverisal
		on click:yield 1 TweetCoin
		on click:anim icon wobble
		icon:https://github.com/Kaydead/Tweet-Clicker/raw/main/twitter-icon-83.png
 		no text
		class:bigButton
		tooltip origin:bottom
		tooltip class:red
