Buildings
	*TEMPLATE
		on click:anim glow
 
	*MemeGenerator|MemeGenerators
		name:Meme Generator|Meme Generators
		text:Meme Generators[?(MemeGenerator >= 0)|s|]
		desc:Creats and sends memes to twitter<//><b>Effect:</b><.>Produces 1 TweetCoin per second.
		icon:https://github.com/Kaydead/Tweet-Clicker/raw/main/1245392-middle.png
		cost:100 TweetCoins
		on tick:yield 1 TweetCoin
		req:100 TweetCoins:earned
​
	*SpamBot|SpamBots
		name:Spam Bot|Spam Bots
		text:Spam Bot[?(SpamBot>= 0)|s|]
		desc:Spams twitter with tweets rapidly.<//><b>Effect:</b><.>Produces 10 TweetCoin per second.
		icon:https://github.com/Kaydead/Tweet-Clicker/raw/main/48px-Gnome-stock_person_bot.svg.png
		cost:500 TweetCoins
		on tick:yield 10 TweetCoins
		req:600 TweetCoins:earned and (MemeGenerator>= 5)
​
	*PremSpamBot|PremSpamBots
		name:PremiumSpamBot|PremiumSpamBots
		text:PremiumSpamBot[?(PremiumSpamBot>= 0)|s|]
		desc:Reply's to other tweets.<//><b>Effect:</b><.>Produces 50 TweetCoin per second.
		icon:https://github.com/Kaydead/Tweet-Clicker/raw/main/i01_pngaaa.com-5754756.png
		cost:500 TweetCoins
		on tick:yield 50 TweetCoins
		req:(SpamBot>= 10)
